94
00:05:59,864 --> 00:06:00,487
Huh.

95
00:06:02,105 --> 00:06:03,857
Yeah, she was pretty out there.

96
00:06:06,767 --> 00:06:08,370
So, wait a sec.

97
00:06:08,542 --> 00:06:10,772
What happened to her?
Where is she now?

98
00:06:11,206 --> 00:06:12,226
