234
00:14:30,197 --> 00:14:32,220
I think she's involved in pornography--

235
00:14:32,271 --> 00:14:33,890
acting, performing.

236
00:14:33,941 --> 00:14:36,657
I think he knows about it.
It's tearing him up.

237
00:14:36,744 --> 00:14:39,227
That's why we're here.
That's why he came to us.

238
00:14:39,278 --> 00:14:41,264
I don't get it.
Why not tell us?

239
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:44,290
How am I supposed to bring this girl home
when he's not even telling me where to look?

240
00:14:44,341 --> 00:14:47,007
He's trying to protect her.
She's his daughter.

241
00:14:47,138 --> 00:14:48,361
Think about his side.

242
00:14:48,412 --> 00:14:51,438
